---
source: crates/runtime/tests/models/search.rs
description: "SELECT id, answer, array_length(answer_embedding), trunc(_score, 3) as _score  FROM vector_search(qs_view, 'second', answer) order by _score desc, id desc LIMIT 4;"
---
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: _score DESC NULLS FIRST, vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer).id DESC NULLS FIRST, fetch=4                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |   Projection: vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer).id, vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer).answer, array_length(vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer).answer_embedding), trunc(vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer)._score, Int64(3)) AS _score |
|               |     TableScan: vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer) projection=[_score, answer, answer_embedding, id]                                                                                                                                                                         |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [_score@3 DESC, id@0 DESC], fetch=4                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |   SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[_score@3 DESC, id@0 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[CAST(key@2 AS Int64) as id, answer@0 as answer, array_length(data@1) as array_length(vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer).answer_embedding), trunc(1 - distance@3, 3) as _score]                                                                    |
|               |       CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |         RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |           BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |             CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |               S3VectorsQueryExec (INDEX_NAME_1): limit=100                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
